---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-charly-black text-white py-10 mt-auto">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center md:text-left">
    
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charly-red mb-4">Charly Pizza</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400">El mejor sabor directo a tu paladar. Hechas con amor y los mejores ingredientes.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Explorar</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li><a href="/menu" class="hover:text-charly-red transition">Nuestras Pizzas</a></li>
        <li><a href="/ubicacion" class="hover:text-charly-red transition">Sucursales</a></li>
        <li><a href="/aviso-privacidad" class="hover:text-charly-red transition">Aviso de Privacidad</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Contacto</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-400">📞 55-1234-5678</p>
      <p class="text-gray-400">📍 Av. Principal #123, Ciudad</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start gap-4 mt-4">
        <a href="#" class="w-8 h-8 bg-charly-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white hover:text-charly-red transition">F</a>
        <a href="#" class="w-8 h-8 bg-charly-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-white hover:text-charly-red transition">I</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-8 pt-6 text-center text-gray-500">
    <p>&copy; {year} Charly Pizza. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
  </div>
</footer>